        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownFalkreathFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionFalkreath\")",
        "content": "Ancient's Ascent is a high mountain shrine in Falkreath where a dragon roosts above a Word Wall. The climb is hard; the descent is harder if the dragon catches you.",
        "display_name": "Ancient's Ascent - Dragon Lair",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.75,
